body:
I've got several pulls failing travis with errors about this file which I didn't change.

https://travis-ci.org/kubernetes/kubernetes/builds/110367940

```
diff -Naupr -I 'Auto generated by' /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/api/swagger-spec/autoscaling.json /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/_tmp/swagger-spec/autoscaling.json
--- /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/api/swagger-spec/autoscaling.json  2016-02-19 12:51:52.539712100 +0000
+++ /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/_tmp/swagger-spec/autoscaling.json 2016-02-19 12:39:12.079712100 +0000
@@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
 {
   "swaggerVersion": "1.2",
   "apiVersion": "",
-  "basePath": "https://10.10.10.10:443",
+  "basePath": "https://10.10.10.10:6443",
   "resourcePath": "/apis/autoscaling",
   "apis": [
    {
diff -Naupr -I 'Auto generated by' /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/api/swagger-spec/autoscaling_v1.json /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/_tmp/swagger-spec/autoscaling_v1.json
--- /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/api/swagger-spec/autoscaling_v1.json   2016-02-19 12:51:52.535712100 +0000
+++ /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/_tmp/swagger-spec/autoscaling_v1.json  2016-02-19 12:39:12.079712100 +0000
@@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
 {
   "swaggerVersion": "1.2",
   "apiVersion": "autoscaling/v1",
-  "basePath": "https://10.10.10.10:443",
+  "basePath": "https://10.10.10.10:6443",
   "resourcePath": "/apis/autoscaling/v1",
   "apis": [
    {
/home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/api/swagger-spec is out of date. Please run hack/update-swagger-spec.sh
!!! Error in hack/verify-swagger-spec.sh:28
  '"${KUBE_ROOT}/hack/after-build/verify-swagger-spec.sh" "$@"' exited with status 1
Call stack:
  1: hack/verify-swagger-spec.sh:28 main(...)
Exiting with status 1
```

@kubernetes/rh-oncall can you confirm the problem?
@wojtek-t You're usually up early mind taking a look?
